description: Tang Yin (from March 6, 1470 to January 7, 1524), known as Bohu, later changed to Ziwei, and was also known as Liuru Jushi, Taohua Anzhu, Tang Sheng of the State of Lu, and Escaping Zen Immortal Officer.
